POPULARITY

Adaptive media randomplayer for Debian Linux

Copyright 2012-2022 Michael Redman

GPL License

https://github.com/michael-redman/popularity

- Installating Dependencies -

apt install ...

Common: make gcc libssl-dev

Music/Video Shuffler: libpq-dev libavformat-dev sox vlc

Slideshow: libx11-dev libpq-dev xli

- Installing Popularity -

git clone https://github.com/michael-redman/popularity

make && sudo make install

will make and install everything (common files module, music/video player module, slideshow module).

- Data Setup -

See the popularity(7) man page for instructions on setting up a Postgres database to hold your ratings data, importing your music/videos/photos, and setting up the probability distribution cache file.

IN GOD WE TRVST.
